69
00:05:57,281 --> 00:05:58,698
Lucy!

70
00:05:58,783 --> 00:06:00,909
Khoan đã, Lucy, Lucy!

71
00:06:00,993 --> 00:06:02,160
Lucy McClane!

72
00:06:02,244 --> 00:06:05,205
